          "summary": "Tesla plans to offer a subscription service of $30 every month for overnight home charging of electric vehicles in Texas, where windy nights help generate sustainable energy. The service, which will be part of Tesla Electric, is set to offer customers in Texas sustainable energy plans starting in July. Customers usually spend around $56 per month to charge their vehicles at home. Customers must have Tesla's Powerwall energy-storage battery and reside in an approved location in Texas to sign up for the plan.",
